title: War of the Roses: The Alexa Sex List
description: Ben is wondering if his wife is cheating because he found a grocery list on their Alexa that included champagne and condoms.  He asked her about it but she claims she has no idea why that is on the list.  We find out exactly how those items got on the list on this week's War of the Roses!
